  <common_name>Russian knapweed, creeping knapweed, Russian centaurea, mountain-bluet, Turkestan thistle, centaurée de Russie</common_name>
  <derivation>Greek akron , tip, and ptilon , feather, describing the pappus bristles</derivation>
